\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":20401,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2015\/02\/21\/character-silent-mindfulness\/","url_meta":{"origin":11864,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Akhlaq: Allah loves good character, silent reflection","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 21, 2015","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, met Abu Dharr and he said, \u201cO Abu Dharr, shall I not tell you of two qualities that are easy on your back and heavier on the scale of good than others?\u201d Abu Dharr said, \u201cOf course, O\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":20475,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2015\/03\/16\/silent-saved-speaking-evil\/","url_meta":{"origin":11864,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Silence: The silent saved from speaking evil","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 16, 2015","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Amr reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever is silent has been saved.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 2501 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0652\u062f\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0639\u064e\u0645\u0652\u0631\u064d\u0648 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u06